name: The Global NFT's Supper
description:
The milky way's vanity. In the reality of regular discord, our top crypto collectors and artists have gathered for an annual dinner. Many years have passed, and the world of NFT remains unregulated by the government.

Manipulations, trends, and directions.A line of invisible answers about a bright future runs across the entire surface of the table. We don't have the answers, but we do have the ability to ask questions.
